org.sql: SELECT current_relations.* FROM current_relations INNER JOIN current_relation_members ON current_relation_members.relation_id = current_relations.id WHERE current_relations.visible = "$1" AND current_relation_members.member_type = "$2" AND current_relation_members.member_id = "$3" ORDER BY current_relations.id ASC
